# AstraNet Whitepaper

## Abstract
AstraNet is a decentralized testnet integrating blockchain mechanics with AI-driven features.

## Introduction
Inspired by Bitcoin, AstraNet introduces fees, burn, staking, and dynamic pricing.

## Core Design
- Blocks and transactions
- Mining with proof-of-work
- Wallets with RSA keys

## Economy
- Fees (1%)
- Burn (2%)
- Staking rewards
- Supply tracking
- Dynamic price based on active users

## AI Integration
- AI helper for transaction analysis
- Future integration with external AI APIs

## Conclusion
AstraNet demonstrates how blockchain and AI can merge into a transparent, auditable system.
